Updated November     pm



Marvels Agents ofSept PERIOD  ABC

Following his success with The Avengers last summer Joss Whedon has returned to television with Marvels Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D PERIOD After the first preview of the show back in May the excitement has already begun to build for the September premier PERIOD Despite the lack of the big name superheroes there is one character that has become the biggest talk of the new TV series Agent Phil Coulsen PERIOD The beloved agent who has been a part of the franchise since the first Iron Man was killed last summer but is now back along with a cast of new characters to bring an action packed world of superheroes for the fall PERIOD

Once Upon a Time in Wonderland Oct PERIOD  ABC

For those who love the twisting plots of shows like Lost and Once Upon a Time there is a new show to keep you on the edge of your seats PERIOD After glimpsing the world of Wonderland in season one of Once Upon a Time this new spinoff gives viewers a very different look at Alices adventures in Wonderland PERIOD The previews show a grown up Alice rescued from an asylum by the White Rabbit and on her way to save her lost love Cyrus PERIOD The show also includes other well known fantasy characters like the Red Queen and Jafar from Aladdin PERIOD Only time will tell if this show will cast as much of a spell over viewers as its original counterpart PERIOD

The Blacklist Sept PERIOD  NBC

Who is on the Blacklist This is the question lovers of mystery and drama will be asking after NBCs The Blacklist premiers in late September PERIOD The story revolves around the criminal Raymond Reddington the FBIs most wanted as he surrenders to the authorities and requests to speak to one person Elizabeth Keen PERIOD Reddington becomes an unlikely partner to the federal agent as he guides her towards criminals that the government dont even know PERIOD The show has the feel of Silence of the Lambs and sets the stage for twisting plot that will keep viewers guessing PERIOD

Mom Sept PERIOD  and Dads Sept PERIOD  CBS and FOX

Parents are taking over television sitcom on CBS and FOX PERIOD On the CBSs Mom Anna Faris single mom Christy and Allison Janney Bonnie are daughter and mother going headtohead as Christy tries to make a fresh start in Napa Valley PERIOD Over at FOX a similar parentchild clash has also been created by comedy mind Seth MacFarlane PERIOD Seth Green and Giovanni Ribisi play two video game designers whose fathers unexpectedly drop in looking for a place to stay PERIOD Dads has already drawn attention from the crass humor that have been made in the preview PERIOD

Sean Saves the World Oct PERIOD  NBC

Seven years after leaving Will and Grace behind back in  Sean Hayes is back with his own show PERIOD Hayes plays a gay divorced single dad whose teenage daughter moves in with him PERIOD He begins to juggle his careeroriented life and demanding new boss with trying to be the best dad in the world PERIOD The show also stars Hayess SMASH costar Megan Hilty Linda Lavin and Samantha Isler as his daughter Ellie PERIOD
